<!--
    Complex Ethernet topology with 6 ECUs and 3 switches.
    Network layout:
               Switch1 (on ECU_SW1)
              / |    |      \
             /  |    |       \
        ECU_A ECU_B ECU_C   Switch2 (on ECU_SW2)
